ygData.msgSnippet: My favourite mobs so far are either some of the ghost things in the City of Mist or the Ravenous Nibblers in Dalnir. My guild dungeon crawled Dalnir earlier
ygData.messageBody:
My favourite mobs so far are either some of the ghost things in the City of
Mist or the Ravenous Nibblers in Dalnir.

My guild dungeon crawled Dalnir earlier today - didn't find much but its a
really well designed and great looking place. If you can get a level 35
group it would be really worth a trip. Sadly it was a little too low level
for us as we were all level 40+.

Bruen Bladesong
Bard of 40 Songs
Avengers Federation
Erollisi Marr
